{"tid":35811,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一樣臭到嘔既經驗","createTime":"2016-12-12T10:30:05.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-13T08:08:58.000Z","uid":1634,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ba1455333ee190f48cd4dff74b94d5016461e954","tid":35811,"uid":1634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T10:30:05.000Z","msg":"小弟今日上堂，俾坐係隔離隻豬西個口臭到衝咗去廁所嘔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 嘔到而家個喉嚨仲痛緊<br />\n利申隻豬西係全校公認神獸之一<br />\n搞到小弟今日全日要戴住個口罩頂住浸味"},{"pid":"c2b8b24b5b6d2851ee7782cc357b004a1011bf5d","tid":35811,"uid":42097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T10:31:21.000Z","msg":"聞胃液個陣味一定無得輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ec724525a5946446546c69f727b36d68c3ba66c","tid":35811,"uid":36860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T10:36:29.000Z","msg":"屍臭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd2caefaf4e44af54fdd4a4c6e29992ce47f20f1","tid":35811,"uid":15237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T10:40:31.000Z","msg":"D 大陸狗個口好撚臭<br />\n麻甩佬都好臭"},{"pid":"5be7f0fa0d1d9f6a94780a450c4029b8f044084e","tid":35811,"uid":56532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T10:44:16.000Z","msg":"仆你個街，以前中學復活節補課用人地班房<br />\n個櫃筒有盒米粉擺左唔知幾耐<br />\n未打開已經有陣屁味<br />\n一打開臭到成個課室都係屎味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最後要轉課室上堂"},{"pid":"aaaa0610929f32b06324337dcd5f30debe401533","tid":35811,"uid":1634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T10:47:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仆你個街，以前中學復活節補課用人地班房<br />\n個櫃筒有盒米粉擺左唔知幾耐<br />\n未打開已經有陣屁味<br />\n一打開臭到成個課室都係屎味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最後要轉課室上堂</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2f539ce2a1510ab50dc473d0a80bc0774c0836f","tid":35811,"uid":30379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T10:58:01.000Z","msg":"地盤吸屎車炒左"},{"pid":"358ae05bf3b8e5bda0ccc7fc2dd81673cfdfe768","tid":35811,"uid":50744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T11:09:33.000Z","msg":"奶西"},{"pid":"5384623287e1dd16386d29f848384c88c8988a4a","tid":35811,"uid":29371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T11:12:34.000Z","msg":"行過聞到人地有陣頭油味 後尾嘔左兩次<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53ae882dc54c4e725a2338705bc3d2e5f14bd69c","tid":35811,"uid":16951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T11:47:04.000Z","msg":"小學嗰陣見到有同學個頭好油反光嗰種<br />\n覺得會有野聞 所以索左幾野<br />\n嘩屌你老母 味精味<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n事後問返佢點解會咁 佢就答「我成個禮拜無洗頭喇」<br />\n但係佢屋企好窮 所以都無拎嚟做笑柄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"305e5c471d7355c50399612aed6889ce1d2fcd47","tid":35811,"uid":32932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T11:48:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GL56544.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGL56544.jpg&h=e62884d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n尋日開既 第一下真係好少少想嘔"},{"pid":"d44c4f8ee036f7848690ae54a44bec758bc53145","tid":35811,"uid":32932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T11:48:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GL56544.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGL56544.jpg&h=e62884d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n尋日開既 第一下真係好少少想嘔</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有少少"},{"pid":"398a0cd3483fce61e5cde8399e77e649cb96348e","tid":35811,"uid":59715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T11:51:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GL56544.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGL56544.jpg&h=e62884d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n尋日開既 第一下真係好少少想嘔</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有少少</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n邊道有得買"},{"pid":"d4062883afec593c834b25135fa4a724ab558df5","tid":35811,"uid":26592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T11:55:46.000Z","msg":"屋企d金魚死晒<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48deace5933f11253298689d9ea7a5a8171d7c39","tid":35811,"uid":36501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T12:08:24.000Z","msg":"話說有日屋企人買左盒泡菜返黎食<br />\n我阿媽見到就話自己整都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n第2日就買左d娃娃菜同自己整既配料放落個桶度醃<br />\n<br />\n隔左個幾星期之後我見到桶野就諗住打開黎睇下點<br />\n一打開臭到全屋都想嘔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係成世人聞過最撚臭既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6d91b8b0aa58cd6a7e9c1b65833216e45b59a08","tid":35811,"uid":8302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T12:09:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1Qu0nhN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1Qu0nhN.jpg&h=377a85b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n飲左淡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"706bad2b4517ecc4f0b883275b26f10ac9f52243","tid":35811,"uid":17550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T12:09:26.000Z","msg":"那兒來的屎？"},{"pid":"96ce93c6095dc53ed561e198dfbe8bc447299ab0","tid":35811,"uid":54900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T12:11:31.000Z","msg":"依個post令我想啲想嘔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dad67850c70e780877c934af19c3f18b017c405e","tid":35811,"uid":11161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T12:14:52.000Z","msg":"屍臭味"},{"pid":"f